<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset='utf-8'>
    <meta http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible' content='IE=edge'>
    <title>Notepad</title>
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1'>
    <style type="text/css">
        * {
            font-family: Verdana, "Bitstream Vera Sans", sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
            background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAQAAAAECAYAAACp8Z5+AAAAH0lEQVQIW2NgYODjBWJWKOZgQOKwQDAKByLAgSTACQAp6QE8mK8aTgAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==');
        }
        li {
            margin: 7px 0;
        }
        code {
            color: white;
            background-color: #f8bb22;
            padding: 1px 4px;
            border: solid 1px #edb015;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="Box-body p-5">
        <h1>Edith</h1>
        <p>A quick small wiki, perfect for pasting quick texts or code and sharing it between friends.</p>
        <p>Don't worry about saving, it saves at every key stroke. Think of it as a magic zero-UI Web notepad.</p>
        <p>Try it out at <a href="http://edit.sunfox.org/any-page-name"
                rel="nofollow">http://edit.sunfox.org/any-page-name</a>.</p>
        <h2>Usage</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><code>/any-page-name</code>: type what you want, it's saved automagically!</li>
            <li><code>/any-page-name.txt</code>: raw text version.</li>
            <li><code>/any-page-name.html</code>: HTML version through the <a
                    href="http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/" rel="nofollow">Markdown</a> syntax.</li>
            <li><code>/any-page-name.remark</code>: Slideshow version using <a
                    href="https://github.com/gnab/remark">Remark</a>.</li>
            <li><code>/any-page-name.graphviz</code>: Graph version of the dot syntax using <a
                    href="https://github.com/mdaines/viz.js/">Viz</a>, see <a href="http://www.webgraphviz.com/"
                    rel="nofollow">WebGraphViz</a> for examples.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Keyboard shortcut <code>Ctrl</code>+<code>E</code> switches from edit mode to HTML mode.</p>
        <h3>Favicon</h3>
        <p><img src="data:image/gif;base64," alt="Magic Favicon changing as the page updates" style="max-width:100%;"></p>
        <p>The favicon changes as the page updates and is also an indicator that the page is currently saving or not.
        </p>
        <h3>REST</h3>
        <p>Edith is also a RESTful API. So go ahead and try to <code>PUT</code> or <code>DELETE</code> on these URLs.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
